The fix doesn't seem right. I am assuming you would want to obtain the underlying type of the generic instance instead and retry the switch. For example: https://github.com/dotnet/runtime/blob/b312158dc6a79c91109f176cba7a05cc6ed6655c/src/mono/mono/mini/interp/transform.c#L341

