nodes.body:
Ah interesting. This sounds like it's a problem in the (very old) special copy of Cecil we use in the ILStrip task that we can't upgrade for various reasons and moving to System.Reflection.Metadata has been on the backlog for quite some time  (https://github.com/dotnet/runtime-assets/issues/383)

We'd probably need to backport whatever fixes this to https://github.com/dotnet/runtime-assets/tree/main/src/Microsoft.DotNet.CilStrip.Sources, but this definitely won't make it into 10.0

@jamescrosswell if you want to work on this feel free to ping me on Discord and I can give more background.
